
  This directory and its subdirectories contain software for flexible
  Bayesian leaning of regression, classification, and other models 
  based on multilayer perceptron neural networks and Gaussian processes, 
  implemented using Markov chain Monte Carlo methods.  

  For more information, see the files in the 'doc' directory, in particular 
  'manual', or, if you have a Web browser, view 'index.html' in 'doc'.
  
  The contents of this directory and its sub-directories are 
